<div class=Section1>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:
auto;text-align:center'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>DECRETO
DEL PRESIDENTE DELLA REPUBBLICA 3 luglio 2003, n. 222</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:
auto;text-align:center'><span class=GramE><b><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>Regolamento sui contenuti minimi dei piani di sicurezza nei
cantieri temporanei o mobili, in attuazione dell'articolo 31, comma 1, della
leg</span></b></span><b><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>ge 11
febbraio 1994, n. 109.&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:
auto;text-align:center'><i><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Pubblicato
sulla Gazzetta Ufficiale n. 193 del 21 agosto 2003</span></i><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<pre><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span class=GramE><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>testo</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'> in vigore dal:<span
style='color:#AF051F'> </span>5-9-2003</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></pre>

<p><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;IL PRESIDENTE DELLA
REPUBBLICA<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>Visto l'articolo 87 della Costituzione;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt'><span class=GramE><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Visto&nbsp; il&nbsp; decreto
legislativo 14 agosto 1996, n. 494, e successive modificazioni;</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>Visto&nbsp; il&nbsp; decreto&nbsp; legislativo&nbsp; 19 novembre&nbsp;
1999<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; n.&nbsp; 528, ed in particolare l'articolo
22;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt'><span class=GramE><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Visto l'articolo 31, comma 1, della
legge 11 febbraio 1994, n. 109, e successive modificazioni;</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>Sentite&nbsp; le organizzazioni sindacali e imprenditoriali
maggiormente rappresentative;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt'><span class=GramE><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Visto<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>il<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  
</span>decreto<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>legislativo<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>19 settembre<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>1994,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>n.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>626,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>e
successive modificazioni;</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt'><span class=GramE><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Visto l'articolo 17, comma 1, della
legge 23 agosto 1988, n. 400;</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt'><span class=GramE><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Vista<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>la<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>preliminare<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>deliberazione<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>del<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>Consiglio dei Ministri,
adottata nella riunione del 21 settembre 2001;</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt'><span class=GramE><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Acquisito il parere della Conferenza
unificata, di cui all'articolo 8<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>del<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>decreto legislativo 28 agosto
1997, n. 281, reso nella seduta de</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>l 31 gennaio 2002;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt'><span class=GramE><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Udito<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>il<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>parere<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>del<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>Consiglio<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di Stato, espresso
dalla sezione</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>consultiva<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>per<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>gli<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>atti<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>normativi<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>nell'adunanza dell'11 novembre</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>20</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>02;</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt'><span class=GramE><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Vista<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>la<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>deliberazione del Consiglio
dei Ministri, adottata nella</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>riunione del 23 maggio 2003;</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt'><span class=GramE><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Sulla<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>proposta<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>dei Ministri del lavoro
e delle politiche sociali,</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>della salute, delle infrastrutture e
dei trasporti e per le politiche</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>co</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>munitarie;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span class=GramE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>E</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'> m a n a<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span class=GramE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>il</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'> seguente regolamento:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Capo <span class=GramE>I<br>
<br>
DISPOSIZIONI GENERALI</span> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:120%'><b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Art. 1.</span></b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:120%'><b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Definizioni e
termini <span class=GramE>di </span>efficacia</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>1. Ai fini del
presente <span class=GramE>regolamento</span> si intendono per: </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
a) scelte&nbsp;&nbsp; progettuali&nbsp;&nbsp; ed&nbsp; organizzative:&nbsp;
insieme&nbsp; di&nbsp; scelte effettuate&nbsp; in&nbsp; fase&nbsp; di&nbsp;
progettazione dal progettista dell'opera in collaborazione&nbsp; con&nbsp; il
coordinatore per la progettazione, al fine di garantire&nbsp; l'eliminazione&nbsp;
o&nbsp; la&nbsp; riduzione&nbsp; al&nbsp; minimo dei rischi di lavoro.&nbsp; Le&nbsp;
scelte&nbsp; progettuali&nbsp; sono&nbsp; <span class=GramE>effettuate</span>&nbsp;
nel&nbsp; campo&nbsp; delle tecniche&nbsp; costruttive,&nbsp; dei materiali da
impiegare e delle tecnologie da&nbsp; adottare; le scelte organizzative sono
effettuate nel campo della pianificazione temporale e spaziale dei lavori;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
b) procedure:&nbsp; le&nbsp; <span class=GramE>modalità</span> e le sequenze
stabilite per eseguire un determinato lavoro od operazione;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'> <span class=GramE>c)
apprestamenti: le opere provvisionali necessarie ai fini della<span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>tutela della salute e della
sicurezza dei lavoratori in cantiere;</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>d)
attrezzature:<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span>le<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  
</span>attrezzature<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavoro<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>come<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>definite</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span class=GramE><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>all'articolo<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>34,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>comma<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>1</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lettera<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>a),<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>del<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>decreto<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>legislativo</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>19 settembre 1994,
n. 626, e successive modificazioni;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>e) misure<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>preventive<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  
</span>e<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>protettive:<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>gli<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>apprestamenti,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>le</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>attrezzature,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>le<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>infrastrutture,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>i<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>mezzi<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>e servizi di protezione</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>collettiva,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>atti<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>a<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>prevenire<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>il<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>manifestarsi<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>situazioni<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>pericolo,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>a<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>proteggere<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>i<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavoratori da rischio <span class=GramE>di </span>infortunio
ed a</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>tutelare la loro
salute;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>f) prescrizioni<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>operative:<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span>le<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>indicazioni<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  
</span>particolari<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>carattere<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  
</span>temporale,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>comportamentale,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>organizzativo,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>tecnico<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>e</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>procedurale,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>da<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>rispettare durante le fasi critiche del processo di</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>costruzione, <span class=GramE>in relazione
alla</span> complessità dell'opera da realizzare;</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>g) cronoprogramma<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>dei<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>lavori:<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>programma dei lavori in
cui sono</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>indicate,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>in<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>base<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>alla complessità dell'opera,
le lavorazioni, le</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>fasi<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>e<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>le
sottofasi di lavoro, la loro sequenza temporale e la loro</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>durata;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
class=GramE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>h)
PSC:<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>il<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>piano<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span
