(lettera soppressa).».</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;-&nbsp; Il&nbsp; testo del
decreto legislativo 28 agosto 1997, n.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>281&nbsp; (Definizione&nbsp; ed&nbsp;
ampliamento delle attribuzioni della</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Conferenza&nbsp; permanente&nbsp;
per&nbsp; i&nbsp; rapporti&nbsp; tra&nbsp; lo Stato, le regioni&nbsp; e&nbsp;
le&nbsp; province&nbsp; autonome&nbsp; di&nbsp; Trento e Bolzano ed</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>unificazione<span
class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; per&nbsp; le&nbsp; materie&nbsp; ed&nbsp; i compiti
di interesse comune&nbsp; delle&nbsp; regioni, delle province e dei comuni, con
la</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>Conferenza Stato-citta' ed autonomie locali), e' pubblicato</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>nella
Gazzetta Ufficiale 30 agosto 1997, n. 202.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Note all'art. 1:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>-&nbsp; Il&nbsp; testo&nbsp;
dell'art.&nbsp; 34<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; comma&nbsp; 1, lettera a),
del</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>citato decreto legislativo n. 626 del 1994, e' il seguente:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>«1.&nbsp; Agli effetti delle
disposizioni di cui al presente titolo <span class=GramE>si </span>intendono
per:</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a)
attrezzatura&nbsp;&nbsp; di&nbsp;&nbsp; lavoro:&nbsp;&nbsp; qualsiasi&nbsp;
macchina,</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>apparecchio, utensile od impianto destinato ad essere
usato</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>durante il lavoro<span class=GramE>;</span>».</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>-&nbsp; Il testo dell'art. 12 del
citato decreto legislativo</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>n. 494 del 1996, e' il seguente:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>«Art.&nbsp; 12 (Piano di sicurezza e
di coordinamento).&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>1.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'> Il&nbsp;&nbsp; piano&nbsp;&nbsp;
contiene&nbsp;&nbsp; l'individuazione<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;
l'analisi&nbsp; e&nbsp; la</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>valutazione&nbsp; dei&nbsp;
rischi,&nbsp; e&nbsp; le conseguenti procedure, gli</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>apprestamenti
e le attrezzature atti a garantire, per tutta</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>la&nbsp;
durata&nbsp; dei&nbsp; lavori,&nbsp; il&nbsp; rispetto&nbsp; delle&nbsp; norme
per la</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>prevenzione&nbsp; degli&nbsp; infortuni&nbsp; e la tutela
della salute dei</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>lavoratori,&nbsp; nonché&nbsp;
la&nbsp; stima&nbsp; dei relativi costi che non</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>sono&nbsp;
soggetti&nbsp; al&nbsp; ribasso&nbsp; nelle&nbsp; offerte&nbsp; delle&nbsp;
imprese</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>esecutrici.&nbsp;&nbsp; Il&nbsp; piano&nbsp;
contiene&nbsp; altresì&nbsp; le&nbsp; misure&nbsp; di</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>prevenzione&nbsp;
dei rischi risultanti dalla eventuale presenza</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>simultanea&nbsp;
o&nbsp; successiva&nbsp; di più imprese o dei lavoratori</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>autonomi&nbsp;
ed&nbsp; e' redatto anche al fine di prevedere, quando</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>ciò
risulti necessario, l'utilizzazione di impianti comuni</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>quali&nbsp;
infrastrutture,&nbsp; mezzi&nbsp; logistici&nbsp; e&nbsp; di&nbsp; protezione</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>collettiva.
Il piano e' costituito da una relazione tecnica</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>e&nbsp;
prescrizioni&nbsp; correlate&nbsp; alla complessità dell'opera da</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>realizzare&nbsp;
ed alle eventuali fasi critiche del processo di</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>costruzione. In
particolare il piano contiene, <span class=GramE>in relazione<span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>alla</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;
tipologia&nbsp;&nbsp; del&nbsp; cantiere&nbsp; interessato,&nbsp; i&nbsp;
seguenti</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>elementi:</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a) <span
class=GramE>modalità</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; da&nbsp;&nbsp; seguire&nbsp; per&nbsp;
la&nbsp; recinzione&nbsp; del</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>cantiere, gli accessi e le
segnalazioni;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>b)
protezioni&nbsp;&nbsp; o&nbsp;&nbsp; misure&nbsp;&nbsp; di&nbsp;
sicurezza&nbsp; contro&nbsp; i<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>possibili
rischi provenienti dall'ambiente esterno;</span></span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; c) servizi
igienico-assistenziali;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; d)
protezioni&nbsp; o&nbsp; misure&nbsp; di&nbsp; sicurezza connesse alla</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>presenza
nell'area del cantiere di linee aeree e <span class=GramE>condutture</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>sotterranee;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>e</span>)
viabilità principale di cantiere;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; f) impianti&nbsp;
di&nbsp; alimentazione&nbsp; e&nbsp; reti principali <span class=GramE>di<span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span></span>elettricità, acqua, gas ed
energia di qualsiasi tipo;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; g) impianti&nbsp;
di&nbsp; terra&nbsp; e&nbsp; di&nbsp; protezione&nbsp; contro&nbsp; le</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>scariche
atmosferiche;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>h)
misure generali di protezione contro il rischio di<span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman"'> </span>seppellimento da adottare negli scavi;</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; i) misure&nbsp;
generali&nbsp; da adottare contro il rischio <span class=GramE>di<span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span></span>annegamento;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>l)&nbsp;
misure&nbsp; generali di protezione da adottare contro<span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman"'> </span>il rischio di caduta dall'alto;</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>m)
misure&nbsp; per assicurare la salubrità dell'aria nei<span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman"'> </span>lavori in galleria;</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>n)
misure per assicurare la stabilità delle pareti e<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
</span>della volta nei lavori in galleria;</span></span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; o) misure&nbsp;
generali di sicurezza da adottare nel caso</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>
</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>di&nbsp; estese&nbsp;
demolizioni&nbsp; o&nbsp; manutenzioni<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; ove le
modalità</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>tecniche di attuazione siano definite in fase di
progetto;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; p) misure&nbsp;
di&nbsp; sicurezza contro i possibili rischi <span class=GramE>di<span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span></span>incendio&nbsp; o
esplosione connessi con lavorazioni e materiali</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>pericolosi
utilizzati in cantiere;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; q) disposizioni
per dare attuazione a quanto previsto</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>dall'art. 14;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>r)
disposizioni per dare attuazione a quanto previsto<span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman"'> </span>dall'art. 5, comma 1, lettera c);</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; s) valutazione<span
class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; in&nbsp; relazione&nbsp; alla&nbsp;
tipologia&nbsp; dei lavori,&nbsp;&nbsp; delle&nbsp; spese&nbsp;
prevedibili&nbsp; per&nbsp; l'attuazione&nbsp; dei</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>singoli
elementi del piano;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>t)
misure&nbsp; generali&nbsp; di protezione da adottare contro<span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>gli sbalzi eccessivi di
temperatura.</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>2.&nbsp; Il&nbsp; piano&nbsp;
di&nbsp; sicurezza&nbsp; e&nbsp; coordinamento e' parte</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>integrante
del contratto <span class=GramE>di </span>appalto.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>3.&nbsp; I&nbsp; datori&nbsp;
di&nbsp; lavoro&nbsp; delle imprese esecutrici e i</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>lavoratori&nbsp;
autonomi sono tenuti ad attuare quanto previsto</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>nel&nbsp;
piano&nbsp; di&nbsp; cui&nbsp; al&nbsp; comma&nbsp; 1&nbsp; e nel piano
operativo di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>sicurezza.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>4.&nbsp; I datori di lavoro delle
imprese esecutrici <span class=GramE>mettono<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
</span>a&nbsp; disposizione&nbsp; dei&nbsp; rappresentanti per la sicurezza
copia</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>del&nbsp; piano&nbsp; di&nbsp;
sicurezza&nbsp; e&nbsp; di&nbsp; coordinamento e del piano</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>operativo&nbsp;&nbsp;
di&nbsp;&nbsp; sicurezza&nbsp;&nbsp; almeno&nbsp;&nbsp; dieci&nbsp;&nbsp;
giorni&nbsp; prima</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>dell'inizio dei lavori.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>5.&nbsp; L'impresa che si <span
class=GramE>aggiudica i</span> lavori può presentare</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>al&nbsp;
coordinatore&nbsp; per l'esecuzione proposte di integrazione</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>al&nbsp;
piano&nbsp; di&nbsp; sicurezza e di coordinamento, ove ritenga di</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>poter
meglio garantire la sicurezza nel cantiere sulla base</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>della
&nbsp;propria&nbsp; esperienza.&nbsp; In&nbsp; nessun&nbsp; caso&nbsp; le
eventuali</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>integrazioni&nbsp; possono&nbsp; giustificare
modifiche o adeguamento</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>dei prezzi pattuiti.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>6.&nbsp;&nbsp; Le&nbsp;
disposizioni&nbsp; del&nbsp; presente&nbsp; articolo&nbsp; non&nbsp; si</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>applicano&nbsp;&nbsp;
ai&nbsp;&nbsp; lavori&nbsp; la&nbsp; cui&nbsp; esecuzione&nbsp; immediata&nbsp;
e'</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>necessaria&nbsp;&nbsp; per&nbsp;&nbsp; prevenire&nbsp;&nbsp;
incidenti&nbsp; imminenti&nbsp; o&nbsp; per</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>
</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>organizzare urgenti
misure di salvataggio.».</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>-&nbsp; Il&nbsp; testo&nbsp;
dell'art.&nbsp; 31<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; comma 1-bis, della citata
legge n. 109 del 1994, e' il seguente:</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>«<span class=GramE>1-bis.</span>&nbsp;
Entro&nbsp; trenta&nbsp; giorni&nbsp; dall'aggiudicazione,&nbsp; e</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>comunque&nbsp;
prima della consegna dei lavori, l'appaltatore od</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>il&nbsp; concessionario&nbsp;
redige&nbsp; e&nbsp; consegna&nbsp; ai soggetti di cui</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>all'art.
2, comma 2:</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a)
eventuali&nbsp;&nbsp; proposte&nbsp;&nbsp; integrative&nbsp; del&nbsp;
piano&nbsp; di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>sicurezza&nbsp; e&nbsp; di&nbsp;
coordinamento&nbsp; e&nbsp; del&nbsp; piano&nbsp; generale di</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>sicurezza&nbsp;
quando questi ultimi siano previsti ai sensi del</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>decreto
legislativo 14 agosto 1996, n. 494;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; b) un&nbsp;
piano&nbsp; di&nbsp; sicurezza&nbsp; sostitutivo del piano di</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>sicurezza&nbsp;
e&nbsp; di&nbsp; coordinamento&nbsp; e&nbsp; del&nbsp; piano&nbsp; generale di</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>sicurezza,
quando questi ultimi non siano previsti ai sensi</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>del decreto
legislativo 14 agosto 1996, n. 494;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; c) un piano
operativo di sicurezza per quanto attiene</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>alle&nbsp; proprie&nbsp; scelte&nbsp;
autonome&nbsp; e relative responsabilità</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>nell'organizzazione&nbsp; del&nbsp;
cantiere&nbsp; e&nbsp; nell'esecuzione&nbsp; dei</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>lavori<span
class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; da&nbsp;&nbsp; considerare&nbsp;&nbsp;
come&nbsp; piano&nbsp; complementare&nbsp; di</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>dettaglio&nbsp;
del&nbsp; piano&nbsp; di&nbsp; sicurezza&nbsp; e&nbsp; di coordinamento e</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>dell'eventuale&nbsp;
piano&nbsp; generale di sicurezza, quando questi</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>ultimi&nbsp;
siano&nbsp; previsti&nbsp; ai&nbsp; sensi&nbsp; del decreto legislativo</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>14
agosto&nbsp; 1996,&nbsp; n.&nbsp; 494,&nbsp; ovvero&nbsp; del&nbsp; piano di
sicurezza</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>sostitutivo di cui alla lettera b).».</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>-&nbsp; Il&nbsp; testo&nbsp;
dell'art.&nbsp; 2, comma 1, del citato decreto</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>legislativo n.
494 del 1996, e successive modificazioni, e'</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>
</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>il seguente:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>«1.&nbsp; Agli effetti delle
disposizioni di cui al presente</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>decreto <span class=GramE>si </span>intendono
per:</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a)
cantiere&nbsp;&nbsp; temporaneo&nbsp;&nbsp; o&nbsp;&nbsp; mobile<span
class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; in&nbsp; appresso</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>denominato
«cantiere»: qualunque luogo in cui si effettuano</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>lavori&nbsp;
edili&nbsp; o&nbsp; di&nbsp; ingegneria&nbsp; civile&nbsp; il&nbsp; cui elenco
e'</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>riportato all'allegato;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; b)
committente:&nbsp; il&nbsp; soggetto&nbsp; per&nbsp; conto&nbsp; del&nbsp;
quale</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>l'intera&nbsp;&nbsp; opera&nbsp; <span class=GramE>viene</span>&nbsp;
realizzata,&nbsp; indipendentemente&nbsp; da</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>
</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>eventuali&nbsp;
frazionamenti&nbsp; della sua realizzazione. Nel caso</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span class=GramE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>di </span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:
Arial'>appalto di opera pubblica, il committente e' il soggetto</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>titolare&nbsp;
del&nbsp; potere&nbsp; decisionale e di spesa relativo alla</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>gestione
dell'appalto;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; c) responsabile&nbsp;
dei lavori: soggetto che può essere</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>incaricato&nbsp; dal&nbsp;
committente&nbsp; ai fini della progettazione o</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>della&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
esecuzione&nbsp;&nbsp; o&nbsp;&nbsp; del&nbsp;&nbsp; controllo&nbsp;&nbsp;
dell'esecuzione</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>dell'opera.&nbsp; Nel&nbsp;
caso&nbsp; di&nbsp; appalto&nbsp; di&nbsp; opera pubblica, il</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>responsabile&nbsp;
dei&nbsp; lavori&nbsp; e'&nbsp; il&nbsp; responsabile&nbsp; unico&nbsp; del</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>procedimento&nbsp;
ai&nbsp; sensi dell'art. 7 della legge 11 febbraio</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>1994,
n. 109, e successive modifiche;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; d)
lavoratore&nbsp;&nbsp; autonomo: &nbsp;&nbsp;persona&nbsp;&nbsp; fisica&nbsp;
la&nbsp; cui</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>attività&nbsp;&nbsp;
professionale&nbsp;&nbsp; concorre&nbsp;&nbsp; alla&nbsp;&nbsp; <span
class=GramE>realizzazione</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>dell'opera senza vincolo di
subordinazione;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>e)&nbsp;
coordinatore&nbsp; in materia di sicurezza e di salute<span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman"'> </span>durante&nbsp; la progettazione dell'opera, di
seguito denominato<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>coordinatore
per la proget</span>tazione: soggetto incaricato, dal</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>committente&nbsp;
o dal responsabile dei lavori, dell'esecuzione</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>dei compiti di
cui all'art. 4;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>f)
coordinatore&nbsp; in&nbsp; materia di sicurezza e di salute<span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>durante&nbsp; la realizzazione
dell'opera, di seguito denominato<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>coordinatore
per l'esecuzi</span>one dei lavori: soggetto, diverso</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>dal&nbsp;
datore&nbsp; di lavoro dell'impresa esecutrice, incaricato,</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>dal&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;committente&nbsp;&nbsp; o&nbsp;&nbsp; dal&nbsp;&nbsp;
responsabile&nbsp;&nbsp; dei&nbsp;&nbsp; lavori,</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>dell'esecuzione
dei compiti di cui all'art. 5;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>f-bis</span>)&nbsp;
uomini-giorno:&nbsp; entità presunta del cantiere</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>rappresentata&nbsp;&nbsp;
dalla&nbsp;&nbsp; somma&nbsp;&nbsp; delle&nbsp; giornate&nbsp; lavorative</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>prestate&nbsp;
dai&nbsp; lavoratori,&nbsp; anche autonomi, previste per la</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>realizzazione
dell'opera;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>f-ter</span>)
piano operativo di sicurezza: il documento che</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>il&nbsp;
datore&nbsp; di&nbsp; lavoro&nbsp; dell'impresa&nbsp; esecutrice redige, in</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>riferimento&nbsp;
al&nbsp; singolo&nbsp; cantiere&nbsp; interessato,&nbsp; ai&nbsp; sensi</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>dell'art.&nbsp;
4&nbsp; del decreto legislativo 19 settembre 1994, n.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>626,
e successive modifiche.».</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<pre style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></pre>

<p style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Capo
II<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>PIANO
DI SICUREZZA E DI COORDINAMENTO </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Art. 2.</span></b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Contenuti minimi</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>1.&nbsp; Il&nbsp;
PSC&nbsp; e'&nbsp; specifico&nbsp; per&nbsp; ogni singolo cantiere temporaneo o</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>mobile e di concreta fattibilità; i suoi
contenuti <span class=GramE>sono</span> il risultato</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>di&nbsp; scelte&nbsp; progettuali&nbsp;
ed&nbsp; organizzative conformi alle prescrizioni</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>dell'articolo&nbsp; 3 del decreto legislativo 19 settembre
1994, n. 626, e</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>successive
modificazioni.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>2. <span
class=GramE>Il</span> PSC contiene almeno i seguenti elementi:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>a)
l'identificazione&nbsp; e&nbsp; la&nbsp; descrizione&nbsp; dell'opera,
esplicitata</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>con:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>1) l'indirizzo del
cantiere;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>2)&nbsp; la&nbsp;
descrizione&nbsp; del <span class=GramE>contesto</span> in cui e' collocata
l'area di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>cantiere;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>3)&nbsp;&nbsp;
una&nbsp; descrizione&nbsp; sintetica&nbsp; dell'opera<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;
con&nbsp; particolare</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>riferimento&nbsp;
alle&nbsp; scelte progettuali, architettoniche, strutturali e</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>tecnologiche;</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>b)
l'individuazione&nbsp;&nbsp; dei&nbsp; soggetti&nbsp; con&nbsp; compiti&nbsp;
di&nbsp; sicurezza,</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>esplicitata&nbsp;&nbsp;
con&nbsp;&nbsp; l'indicazione&nbsp;&nbsp; dei&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>nominativi</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;
dell'eventuale</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>responsabile dei
lavori, del coordinatore per la sicurezza in fase di</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>progettazione&nbsp; e,&nbsp; qualora&nbsp;
già&nbsp; nominato,&nbsp; del&nbsp; coordinatore per la</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>sicurezza&nbsp; in&nbsp; fase di esecuzione
ed a cura dello stesso coordinatore</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>per&nbsp; l'esecuzione&nbsp; con&nbsp; l'indicazione,&nbsp;
prima dell'inizio dei singoli</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>lavori,&nbsp;
dei nominativi dei datori di lavoro delle imprese esecutrici</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>e dei lavoratori autonomi;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>c) una&nbsp;
relazione&nbsp; concernente&nbsp; l'individuazione<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;
l'analisi e la</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>valutazione&nbsp;&nbsp;
dei&nbsp;&nbsp; rischi&nbsp;&nbsp; concreti&nbsp;&nbsp; in&nbsp;
riferimento&nbsp; all'area&nbsp; ed</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>all'organizzazione&nbsp; del&nbsp; cantiere,&nbsp;
alle&nbsp; lavorazioni&nbsp; ed&nbsp; alle&nbsp; loro</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>interferenze;</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>d) le&nbsp;
scelte&nbsp; progettuali&nbsp; ed&nbsp; organizzative<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;
le&nbsp; procedure, le</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>misure preventive e
protettive, in riferimento:</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
class=GramE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>1)
all'area di cantiere, ai sensi dell'articolo 3, commi 1 e 4;</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
class=GramE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>2)&nbsp;
all'organizzazione&nbsp; del cantiere, ai sensi dell'articolo 3,</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>commi 2 e 4;</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
class=GramE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>3)
alle lavorazioni, ai sensi dell'articolo 3, commi 3 e 4;</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>e) le&nbsp;
prescrizioni&nbsp; operative, le misure preventive e protettive</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>ed&nbsp; i&nbsp; dispositivi&nbsp; di&nbsp;
protezione&nbsp; individuale<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; in riferimento
alle</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>interferenze tra le
lavorazioni, ai sensi dell'articolo 4, commi 1, 2</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>e 3;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>f) le misure di
coordinamento <span class=GramE>relative all'</span>uso comune da parte di</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>più&nbsp; imprese&nbsp; e&nbsp;
lavoratori&nbsp; autonomi, come scelta di pianificazione</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
class=GramE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>lavori</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;
finalizzata&nbsp; alla&nbsp; sicurezza, di apprestamenti, attrezzature,</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>infrastrutture,&nbsp; mezzi&nbsp; e&nbsp;
servizi&nbsp; di&nbsp; protezione&nbsp; collettiva di cui</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>all'articolo 4, commi 4 e 5;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>g) le&nbsp;&nbsp; <span
class=GramE>modalità</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; organizzative&nbsp;&nbsp;
della&nbsp;&nbsp; cooperazione&nbsp;&nbsp; e&nbsp; del</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>coordinamento,&nbsp; nonché della reciproca
informazione, fra i datori di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>lavoro
e tra questi ed i lavoratori autonomi;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>h)
l'organizzazione&nbsp; prevista per il servizio di pronto soccorso,</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>antincendio&nbsp; ed&nbsp;
evacuazione&nbsp; dei&nbsp; lavoratori<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;
nel&nbsp; caso&nbsp; in&nbsp; cui il</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>servizio&nbsp; di&nbsp; gestione delle emergenze e' di tipo
comune, nonché nel</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>caso&nbsp; di&nbsp;
cui&nbsp; all'articolo&nbsp; 17,&nbsp; comma&nbsp; 4,&nbsp; del&nbsp; decreto
legislativo</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>14 agosto&nbsp;
1996,&nbsp; n. 494, e successive modificazioni; il PSC contiene</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>anche&nbsp;&nbsp; i&nbsp;&nbsp;
riferimenti&nbsp;&nbsp; telefonici&nbsp; delle&nbsp; strutture&nbsp;
previste&nbsp; sul</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>territorio&nbsp;
al&nbsp; servizio&nbsp; del&nbsp; pronto&nbsp; soccorso&nbsp; e&nbsp; della
prevenzione</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>incendi;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>i) la&nbsp; durata
prevista delle lavorazioni, delle fasi di lavoro e,</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>quando&nbsp; la&nbsp; complessità&nbsp;
dell'opera&nbsp; lo richieda, delle sottofasi di</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>lavoro<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; che&nbsp;
costituiscono&nbsp; il&nbsp; cronoprogramma&nbsp; dei&nbsp; lavori, nonché</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>l'entità presunta del cantiere espressa in
uomini-giorno;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
class=GramE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>l)
la stima dei costi della sicurezza, ai sensi dell'articolo 7.</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>3.&nbsp; Il&nbsp;
coordinatore&nbsp; per&nbsp; la&nbsp; progettazione indica <span class=GramE>nel</span>
PSC, ove la</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>particolarità&nbsp;
delle&nbsp; lavorazioni&nbsp; lo richieda, il tipo di procedure</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>complementari&nbsp; e&nbsp; di&nbsp;
dettaglio&nbsp; al PSC stesso e connesse alle scelte</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>autonome dell'impresa esecutrice, da
esplicitare nel POS.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>4.&nbsp; <span
class=GramE>Il</span> PSC e' corredato da tavole esplicative di progetto,
relative</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>agli&nbsp; aspetti
della sicurezza, comprendenti almeno una planimetria e,</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>ove&nbsp; la particolarità dell'opera lo
richieda, un profilo altimetrico</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>e&nbsp;
una&nbsp; breve&nbsp; descrizione&nbsp; delle&nbsp; caratteristiche
idrogeologiche del</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>terreno o il rinvio
a specifica relazione se già redatta.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>5.&nbsp;
L'elenco&nbsp; indicativo e non esauriente degli elementi essenziali</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>utili&nbsp; alla&nbsp; definizione&nbsp;
dei contenuti <span class=GramE>del</span> PSC di cui al comma 2, e'</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>riportato nell'allegato I.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p align=center style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:center'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>_______________________________________________<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Note all'art. 2:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>-&nbsp; Il&nbsp; testo dell'art. 3
del citato decreto legislativo</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>n. 626 del 1994, e' il seguente:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>«Art.&nbsp; 3&nbsp; (Misure&nbsp;
generali&nbsp; di tutela).</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>1. &nbsp;Le misure generali&nbsp; per
la protezione della salute e</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>per la sicurezza dei lavoratori sono:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a)
valutazione&nbsp;&nbsp; dei&nbsp;&nbsp; rischi&nbsp; per&nbsp; la&nbsp;
salute&nbsp; e&nbsp; la</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>sicurezza;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'> b) eliminazione&nbsp;&nbsp; dei&nbsp;&nbsp;
rischi&nbsp;&nbsp; in&nbsp;&nbsp; relazione&nbsp; alle</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>conoscenze&nbsp;
acquisite&nbsp; in&nbsp; base al progresso tecnico e, ove</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>ciò
non e' possibile, loro riduzione al minimo;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; c) riduzione dei
rischi alla fonte;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; d)
programmazione&nbsp; della&nbsp; prevenzione&nbsp; mirando&nbsp; ad un</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>complesso
che integra in modo coerente nella prevenzione le</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>condizioni&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
tecniche&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; produttive&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ed&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
organizzative</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>dell'azienda&nbsp; <span class=GramE>nonché</span>
l'influenza dei fattori dell'ambiente</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>di lavoro;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>e</span>)
sostituzione&nbsp; di&nbsp; ciò&nbsp; che e' pericoloso con ciò</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>che
non lo e', o e' meno pericoloso;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; f) rispetto&nbsp;
dei principi ergonomici nella concezione</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>dei&nbsp; posti&nbsp; di&nbsp; lavoro<span
class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; nella&nbsp; scelta delle attrezzature e</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>nella&nbsp;
definizione dei metodi di lavoro e produzione, anche</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>per
attenuare il lavoro monotono e quello ripetitivo;</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>g)
priorità&nbsp; delle&nbsp; misure&nbsp; di protezione collettiva<span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>rispetto alle misure di
protezione individuale;</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; h)
limitazione&nbsp; al&nbsp; minimo&nbsp; del numero dei lavoratori</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>che
sono, o che possono essere, esposti al rischio;</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>i)
utilizzo&nbsp; limitato&nbsp; degli agenti chimici, fisici e<span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>biologici, sui luoghi di lavoro;</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; l) controllo
sanitario dei lavoratori in funzione dei</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>rischi specifici;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; m)
allontanamento&nbsp; del&nbsp; lavoratore dall'esposizione a</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>rischio,
per motivi sanitari inerenti <span class=GramE>la</span> sua persona;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; n) misure
igieniche;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>o</span>)
misure di protezione collettiva ed individuale;</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; p) misure&nbsp;
di&nbsp; emergenza da attuare in caso di pronto</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>soccorso<span
class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; di&nbsp;&nbsp; lotta&nbsp;&nbsp;
antincendio,&nbsp; di&nbsp; evacuazione&nbsp; dei</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>lavoratori e di
pericolo grave ed immediato;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; q) uso di segnali <span
class=GramE>di </span>avvertimento e di sicurezza;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; r)&nbsp;
regolare&nbsp; manutenzione <span class=GramE>di </span>ambienti, attrezzature,</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>macchine&nbsp;&nbsp;
ed&nbsp;&nbsp; impianti,&nbsp;&nbsp; con&nbsp;&nbsp; particolare&nbsp;
riguardo&nbsp; ai</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>dispositivi&nbsp; di&nbsp;
sicurezza&nbsp; in conformità alla indicazione</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>dei fabbricanti;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; s) informazione<span
class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; formazione,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
consultazione&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; e</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>partecipazione&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
dei&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; lavoratori&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ovvero&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
dei&nbsp;&nbsp; loro</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>rappresentanti,&nbsp; sulle questioni
riguardanti la sicurezza e</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>la salute sul luogo
di&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; lavoro;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; t) istruzioni
adeguate ai lavoratori.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>2.&nbsp; Le&nbsp; misure&nbsp;
relative&nbsp; alla sicurezza, all'igiene ed</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>
</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>alla&nbsp; salute&nbsp;
durante&nbsp; il&nbsp; lavoro non <span class=GramE>devono</span> in nessun
caso</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>comportare oneri finanziari per i lavoratori.».</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>-&nbsp; Il&nbsp; testo&nbsp; <span
class=GramE>dell'art. 17, comma 4</span>, del citato decreto</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>legislativo
n. 494 del 1996, e' il seguente:</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>«4.&nbsp;&nbsp; I&nbsp; datori&nbsp;
di&nbsp; lavoro<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; quando&nbsp; e'&nbsp; previsto&nbsp;
nei</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>contratti di affidamento dei lavori che il committente o il</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>responsabile&nbsp;
dei&nbsp; lavori&nbsp; organizzi&nbsp; apposito&nbsp; servizio di</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>pronto
soccorso, antincendio ed evacuazione dei lavoratori,</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>sono&nbsp;
esonerati&nbsp; da&nbsp; quanto&nbsp; previsto dall'art. 4, comma 5,</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>lettera
a), del decreto legislativo n. 626 del 1994.».</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Art. 3.&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Contenuti minimi <span
class=GramE>del</span> PSC in riferimento all'area di cantiere,
all'organizzazione del cantiere, alle lavorazioni</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>1.&nbsp; In&nbsp;
riferimento all'area di cantiere, <span class=GramE>il</span> PSC contiene
l'analisi</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>degli elementi
essenziali di cui all'allegato II, in relazione:</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
a) alle caratteristiche dell'area di cantiere;</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
b) all'eventuale&nbsp; presenza&nbsp; di&nbsp; fattori&nbsp; esterni&nbsp;
che&nbsp; comportano</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>rischi per il
cantiere;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
c) agli&nbsp; eventuali&nbsp; rischi che le lavorazioni di cantiere possono</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>comportare per l'area circostante.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>2.&nbsp; <span
class=GramE>In</span> riferimento all'organizzazione del cantiere il PSC
contiene,</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>in&nbsp;
relazione&nbsp; alla tipologia del cantiere, l'analisi oltre che degli</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>elementi&nbsp; indicati nell'articolo 12,
comma 1, del decreto legislativo</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>14
agosto&nbsp; 1996,&nbsp; n.&nbsp; 494,&nbsp; e&nbsp; successive&nbsp;
modificazioni,&nbsp; anche&nbsp; dei</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>seguenti:</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
a) le&nbsp; eventuali&nbsp; <span class=GramE>modalità</span> di accesso dei
mezzi di fornitura dei</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>materiali;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
b) la dislocazione degli impianti di cantiere;</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; c)
la dislocazione delle zone di carico e scarico;</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span
class=GramE>d) le&nbsp; zone&nbsp; di deposito attrezzature e di stoccaggio
materiali e<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>dei rifiuti;</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
e) le&nbsp; eventuali&nbsp; zone&nbsp; di&nbsp; deposito&nbsp; dei&nbsp;
materiali con pericolo</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>d'incendio o <span
class=GramE>di </span>esplosione.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>3.&nbsp;&nbsp;
In&nbsp; riferimento&nbsp; alle&nbsp; lavorazioni<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;
il&nbsp; coordinatore&nbsp; per&nbsp; la</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>progettazione&nbsp; suddivide&nbsp; le singole lavorazioni
in fasi di lavoro e,</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>quando&nbsp;
la&nbsp; complessità&nbsp; dell'opera&nbsp; lo&nbsp; richiede,&nbsp; in&nbsp;
sottofasi di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>lavoro,&nbsp;&nbsp;
ed&nbsp;&nbsp; effettua&nbsp;&nbsp; l'analisi&nbsp;&nbsp; dei&nbsp;
rischi&nbsp; presenti,&nbsp; facendo</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>particolare&nbsp; attenzione&nbsp; oltre&nbsp; che&nbsp; ai
rischi connessi agli elementi</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>indicati&nbsp;
nell'articolo&nbsp; 12,&nbsp; comma 1, del decreto legislativo n. 494</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>del 1996 e successive modificazioni, anche
ai seguenti:</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
a) al&nbsp; rischio <span class=GramE>di </span>investimento da veicoli
circolanti nell'area di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>cantiere;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
b) al rischio <span class=GramE>di </span>elettrocuzione;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
c) al rischio rumore;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
d) al rischio dall'uso di sostanze chimiche.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>4.&nbsp; Per ogni
elemento dell'analisi di cui ai commi 1, 2 e 3, <span class=GramE>il</span> PSC</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>contiene:</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
a) le&nbsp; scelte&nbsp; progettuali&nbsp; ed&nbsp; organizzative<span
class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; le&nbsp; procedure, le misure&nbsp; preventive&nbsp;
e protettive richieste per eliminare o ridurre al</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>minimo&nbsp; i&nbsp; rischi&nbsp; di lavoro; ove necessario,
vanno prodotte tavole e</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>disegni tecnici
esplicativi;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span
class=GramE>b) le&nbsp; misure&nbsp; di coordinamento atte a realizzare quanto
previsto<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>alla lettera a).</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'>&nbsp;<b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Art. 4. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Contenuti minimi <span
class=GramE>del</span> PSC in riferimento alle interferenze</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>tra le lavorazioni ed al loro coordinamento</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>1.&nbsp; Il&nbsp;
coordinatore&nbsp; per la progettazione <span class=GramE>effettua</span>
l'analisi delle</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>interferenze&nbsp;
tra&nbsp; le&nbsp; lavorazioni,&nbsp; anche&nbsp; quando&nbsp; sono&nbsp;
dovute alle</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>lavorazioni&nbsp;
di&nbsp; una&nbsp; stessa&nbsp; impresa&nbsp; esecutrice &nbsp;o alla presenza
di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>lavoratori&nbsp;
autonomi,&nbsp; e predispone il cronoprogramma dei lavori.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Per le opere rientranti nel campo <span
class=GramE>di </span>applicazione della legge 11 febbraio</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>1994,&nbsp; n.&nbsp; 109,&nbsp; e&nbsp;
successive&nbsp; modificazioni,&nbsp; il cronoprogramma dei</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>lavori&nbsp; ai&nbsp; sensi&nbsp; del
presente regolamento, prende esclusivamente in</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>considerazione&nbsp; le problematiche inerenti gli aspetti
della sicurezza</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>ed&nbsp; e'&nbsp;
redatto&nbsp; ad integrazione del cronoprogramma delle lavorazioni</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>previsto dall'articolo 42 del decreto del
Presidente della Repubblica</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>21
dicembre 1999, n. 554.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>2.&nbsp; In&nbsp;
riferimento&nbsp; alle&nbsp; interferenze&nbsp; tra le lavorazioni, <span
class=GramE>il</span> PSC</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>
</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>contiene&nbsp;
le&nbsp; prescrizioni&nbsp; operative&nbsp; per&nbsp; lo&nbsp; sfasamento
spaziale o</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>temporale&nbsp;
delle&nbsp; lavorazioni interferenti e le modalità di verifica</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>del&nbsp; rispetto di tali prescrizioni;
nel caso in cui permangono rischi</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>di&nbsp; interferenza,&nbsp; indica&nbsp; le&nbsp;
misure&nbsp; preventive&nbsp; e&nbsp; protettive ed i</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>dispositivi&nbsp; di protezione individuale,
atti a ridurre al minimo tali</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>rischi.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>3.&nbsp;
Durante&nbsp; i periodi di maggior rischio dovuto ad interferenze di</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>lavoro<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;
il&nbsp; coordinatore&nbsp; per&nbsp; l'esecuzione verifica periodicamente,</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>previa&nbsp; consultazione&nbsp;
della&nbsp; direzione&nbsp; dei&nbsp; lavori,&nbsp; delle&nbsp; imprese</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>esecutrici&nbsp; e&nbsp; dei lavoratori
autonomi interessati, la compatibilità</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>della&nbsp; relativa&nbsp; parte di PSC con l'andamento dei
lavori, aggiornando</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>il&nbsp;&nbsp;
piano&nbsp; ed&nbsp; in&nbsp; particolare&nbsp; il&nbsp; cronoprogramma&nbsp;
dei&nbsp; lavori,&nbsp; se</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>
</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>necessario.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>4.&nbsp;&nbsp;
Le&nbsp;&nbsp; misure&nbsp;&nbsp; di&nbsp; coordinamento&nbsp; relative&nbsp;
all'uso&nbsp; comune&nbsp; <span class=GramE>di<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
</span></span>apprestamenti,&nbsp; attrezzature,&nbsp; infrastrutture,&nbsp;
mezzi&nbsp; e&nbsp; servizi&nbsp; di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>protezione&nbsp; collettiva,&nbsp; sono definite analizzando
il loro uso comune</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>da parte di più
imprese e lavoratori autonomi.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>5. Il coordinatore
per l'esecuzione dei lavori <span class=GramE>integra il</span> PSC con i</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>nominativi&nbsp; delle imprese esecutrici e
dei lavoratori autonomi tenuti</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>ad&nbsp;
attivare quanto previsto al comma 4 dell'articolo 3 ed al comma 4</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>del&nbsp;&nbsp; presente&nbsp;&nbsp;
articolo&nbsp;&nbsp; e,&nbsp; previa&nbsp; consultazione&nbsp; delle&nbsp;
imprese</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>esecutrici&nbsp; e
dei lavoratori autonomi interessati, indica la relativa</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>cronologia di attuazione e le modalità di
verifica.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p align=center style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:center'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>________________________________________________<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Nota all'art. 4:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>-&nbsp; Il&nbsp; testo&nbsp;
dell'art.&nbsp; 42&nbsp; del decreto del Presidente</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>della&nbsp;
Repubblica&nbsp; 21 dicembre 1999, n. 554 (Regolamento <span class=GramE>di<span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span></span>attuazione&nbsp;
della&nbsp; legge&nbsp; 11 febbraio&nbsp; 1994,&nbsp; n. 109, legge</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>quadro&nbsp;&nbsp;
in&nbsp;&nbsp; materia&nbsp; di&nbsp; lavori&nbsp; pubblici,&nbsp; e&nbsp;
successive</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>modificazioni), e' il seguente:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>«Art.&nbsp; 42&nbsp;
(Cronoprogramma).</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>1. Il progetto esecutivo e'&nbsp;
corredato dal cronoprogramma</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>delle lavorazioni, redatto
&nbsp;al&nbsp; fine&nbsp; di&nbsp; stabilire&nbsp; in&nbsp; via&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>convenzionale,
nel caso di lavori compensati a prezzo chiuso,</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>l'importo degli
stessi da&nbsp; eseguire&nbsp; per&nbsp; ogni&nbsp; anno&nbsp; intero</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>decorrente
dalla data della consegna.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>2.&nbsp; Nei&nbsp; casi&nbsp;
di&nbsp; appalto-concorso&nbsp; e&nbsp; di&nbsp; appalto&nbsp; di</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>progettazione
esecutiva ed esecuzione, il cronoprogramma e'</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>presentato
dall'appaltatore unitamente all'offerta.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>3.&nbsp; Nel&nbsp; calcolo&nbsp;
del&nbsp; tempo&nbsp; contrattuale deve tenersi</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>conto&nbsp;
della&nbsp; prevedibile incidenza dei giorni <span class=GramE>di </span>andamento</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>stagionale
sfavorevole.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>4.&nbsp; Nel caso di sospensione o di
ritardo dei lavori per</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>fatti&nbsp; imputabili&nbsp;
all'impresa<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; resta&nbsp; fermo&nbsp; lo sviluppo</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>esecutivo
risultante dal cronoprogramma.».</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<pre style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></pre>

<p style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Capo
III<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>PIANO
<span class=GramE>DI SICUREZZA SOSTITUTIVO</span> E PIANO OPERATIVO DI
SICUREZZA </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Art. 5.</span></b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Contenuti minimi del
piano di sicurezza sostitutivo&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>1.&nbsp; Il&nbsp;
PSS<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; redatto a cura dell'appaltatore o del
concessionario, contiene&nbsp; gli stessi elementi del PSC di cui all'articolo
2, comma 2, con esclusione della stima dei costi della sicurezza.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<pre><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></pre>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:120%'><b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Art. 6.&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Contenuti minimi del
piano operativo di <span class=GramE>sicurezza</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>1.&nbsp; Il&nbsp;
POS&nbsp; e'&nbsp; redatto&nbsp; a&nbsp; cura di ciascun datore di lavoro delle</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>imprese&nbsp; esecutrici, ai sensi
dell'articolo 4 del decreto legislativo</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>19 settembre 1994, n. 626, e successive modificazioni, <span
class=GramE>in</span> riferimento</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>al&nbsp; singolo&nbsp; cantiere&nbsp; interessato;&nbsp;
esso&nbsp; contiene almeno i seguenti</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>elementi:</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
a) i&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; dati&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; identificativi&nbsp;&nbsp;
dell'impresa&nbsp;&nbsp; esecutrice<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; che</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>comprendono:</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>1)&nbsp; il&nbsp; <span
class=GramE>nominativo</span>&nbsp; del&nbsp; datore&nbsp; di&nbsp; lavoro, gli
indirizzi ed i</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>riferimenti
telefonici della sede legale e degli uffici di cantiere;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>2)&nbsp; la&nbsp;
specifica&nbsp; attività e le singole lavorazioni svolte in</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>cantiere&nbsp;&nbsp;
dall'impresa&nbsp;&nbsp; esecutrice&nbsp;&nbsp; e&nbsp;&nbsp; dai&nbsp;&nbsp;
lavoratori&nbsp; autonomi</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>
</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>subaffidatari;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>3)&nbsp; i&nbsp; <span
class=GramE>nominativi</span> degli addetti al pronto soccorso, antincendio</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>ed&nbsp; evacuazione&nbsp; dei&nbsp;
lavoratori&nbsp; e,&nbsp; comunque,&nbsp; alla&nbsp; gestione delle</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>emergenze&nbsp; in&nbsp; cantiere,&nbsp;
del&nbsp; rappresentante&nbsp; dei&nbsp; lavoratori per la</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>sicurezza, aziendale o territoriale, ove
eletto o designato;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>4) il <span
class=GramE>nominativo</span> del medico competente ove previsto;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>5) il <span
class=GramE>nominativo</span> del responsabile del servizio di prevenzione e</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>protezione;</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>6)&nbsp; i&nbsp; <span
class=GramE>nominativi</span>&nbsp; del&nbsp; direttore&nbsp; tecnico&nbsp;
di&nbsp; cantiere&nbsp; e del</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>capocantiere;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
class=GramE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>7)
il numero e le relative qualifiche dei lavoratori dipendenti</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>dell'impresa&nbsp;&nbsp; esecutrice&nbsp;
e&nbsp; dei&nbsp; lavoratori&nbsp; autonomi&nbsp; operanti&nbsp; in</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>cantie</span></span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>re per conto della stessa impresa;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
b) le&nbsp; specifiche&nbsp; mansioni<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;
inerenti&nbsp; la&nbsp; sicurezza,&nbsp; svolte in</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>cantiere da ogni figura nominata allo scopo
dall'impresa esecutrice;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
c) la&nbsp; descrizione&nbsp; dell'attività'&nbsp; di&nbsp; cantiere, delle <span
class=GramE>modalità</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>organizzative
e dei turni di lavoro;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
d) l'elenco&nbsp; dei&nbsp; ponteggi, dei ponti su ruote a torre e <span
class=GramE>di </span>altre</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>opere&nbsp;
provvisionali&nbsp; di&nbsp; notevole importanza, delle macchine e degli</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>impianti utilizzati nel cantiere;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span
class=GramE>e) l'elenco&nbsp; delle sostanze e preparati pericolosi utilizzati
nel<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>cantiere con le relative
schede di sicurezza;</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;f) l'esito del rapporto di valutazione <span class=GramE>del</span>
rumore;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
g) l'individuazione&nbsp;&nbsp; delle&nbsp;&nbsp; misure&nbsp;&nbsp;
preventive&nbsp; e&nbsp; protettive,</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>integrative&nbsp; rispetto&nbsp; a&nbsp; quelle&nbsp;
contenute&nbsp; <span class=GramE>nel</span> PSC quando previsto,</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>adottate&nbsp; in relazione ai rischi
connessi alle proprie lavorazioni in</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>cantiere;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
h) le&nbsp; procedure&nbsp; complementari e di dettaglio, richieste <span
class=GramE>dal</span> PSC</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>
</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>quando
previsto;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span
class=GramE>i) l'elenco&nbsp; dei dispositivi di protezione individuale forniti
ai<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>lavoratori occupati in
cantiere;</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span
class=GramE>l) la&nbsp;&nbsp; documentazione&nbsp;&nbsp; in&nbsp;&nbsp;
merito&nbsp;&nbsp; all'informazione&nbsp; ed&nbsp; alla<span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman"'> </span>formazione fornite ai lavoratori occupati in
cantiere.</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>2.&nbsp; Ove&nbsp;
non&nbsp; sia&nbsp; prevista&nbsp; la&nbsp; redazione&nbsp; <span class=GramE>del</span>
PSC, il PSS, quando</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>previsto, e'
integrato con gli elementi del POS.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p align=center style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:center'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>____________________________________________<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Nota all'art. 6:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>-&nbsp; Il&nbsp; testo dell'art. 4
del citato decreto legislativo</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>n. 626 del 1994, e' il seguente:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>«Art. 4 (Obblighi del datore di
lavoro, del dirigente e</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>del&nbsp; preposto).</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>1. Il datore di lavoro, <span
class=GramE>in relazione alla</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>natura&nbsp;&nbsp; dell'attività'
&nbsp;&nbsp;dell'azienda&nbsp; ovvero&nbsp; dell'unita'</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>produttiva,
valuta tutti i rischi per la sicurezza e per la</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>salute&nbsp;
dei&nbsp; lavoratori,&nbsp; ivi&nbsp; compresi&nbsp; quelli riguardanti</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>gruppi&nbsp;
di&nbsp; lavoratori&nbsp; esposti a rischi particolari, anche</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>nella&nbsp;
scelta delle attrezzature di lavoro e delle sostanze</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>o&nbsp;&nbsp;
dei&nbsp;&nbsp; preparati&nbsp;&nbsp; chimici&nbsp;&nbsp;
impiegati,&nbsp;&nbsp; nonché&nbsp; nella</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>sistemazione dei luoghi di lavoro.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>2.&nbsp; All'esito&nbsp; della&nbsp;
valutazione di cui al comma 1, il</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>datore di lavoro elabora un documento
contenente:</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a) una&nbsp;
relazione sulla valutazione dei rischi per la</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>sicurezza&nbsp;
e&nbsp; la salute durante il lavoro, nella quale sono</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>specificati
i criteri adottati per la valutazione stessa;</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>b)
l'individuazione&nbsp; delle misure di prevenzione e di<span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman"'> </span>protezione&nbsp; e&nbsp; dei&nbsp; dispositivi&nbsp;
di protezione individuale,<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>conseguente
alla valutazio</span>ne di cui alla lettera a);</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>c)
il&nbsp; programma&nbsp; delle misure ritenute opportune per<span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>garantire&nbsp;&nbsp; il&nbsp;
miglioramento&nbsp; nel&nbsp; tempo&nbsp; dei&nbsp; livelli&nbsp; di<span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>sicurezza.</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>3.&nbsp; Il&nbsp; documento&nbsp; e'
custodito presso l'azienda ovvero</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>l'unita' produttiva.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>4. Il datore di lavoro:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a)
designa&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; il&nbsp;&nbsp; responsabile&nbsp;&nbsp;
del&nbsp;&nbsp; servizio&nbsp;&nbsp; di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>prevenzione&nbsp; e&nbsp;
protezione&nbsp; interno&nbsp; o&nbsp; esterno all'azienda</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>secondo
le regole di cui all'art. 8;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; b) designa&nbsp;
gli&nbsp; addetti al servizio di prevenzione e</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>protezione&nbsp;
interno o esterno all'azienda secondo le regole</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>di cui all'art.
8;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; c) nomina<span
class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; nei casi previsti dall'art. 16, il medico</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>competente.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>5.&nbsp; Il datore di lavoro adotta
le misure necessarie per</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>la sicurezza e la salute dei
lavoratori, e in particolare:</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a) designa&nbsp;
preventivamente&nbsp; i&nbsp; lavoratori incaricati</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>dell'attuazione
delle misure di prevenzione incendi e lotta</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>
</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>antincendio<span
class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; di&nbsp; evacuazione&nbsp; dei&nbsp;
lavoratori&nbsp; in&nbsp; caso di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>pericolo&nbsp; grave&nbsp; e&nbsp;
immediato,&nbsp; di&nbsp; salvataggio,&nbsp; di pronto</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>soccorso
e, comunque, di gestione dell'emergenza;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; b) aggiorna&nbsp;
le misure di prevenzione <span class=GramE>in relazione ai</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>mutamenti
organizzativi e produttivi che hanno rilevanza ai</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>fini&nbsp;
della&nbsp; salute e della sicurezza del lavoro, ovvero in</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>relazione&nbsp;
al&nbsp; grado&nbsp; di&nbsp; evoluzione&nbsp; della&nbsp; tecnica&nbsp; della</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>prevenzione
e della protezione;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; c)&nbsp;
nell'affidare i compiti ai lavoratori tiene conto</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>delle capacità e
delle condizioni degli stessi in rapporto</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>alla loro salute e alla sicurezza;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; d)
fornisce&nbsp;&nbsp; ai&nbsp; lavoratori&nbsp; i&nbsp; necessari&nbsp; e&nbsp;
idonei</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>dispositivi&nbsp;&nbsp; di&nbsp;&nbsp; protezione
&nbsp;&nbsp;individuale<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;
sentito&nbsp;&nbsp; il</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>responsabile del servizio di
prevenzione e protezione;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; e) prende&nbsp; le
misure appropriate affinché soltanto i</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>lavoratori&nbsp; che hanno ricevuto
adeguate istruzioni <span class=GramE>accedano</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>alle
zone che li espongono ad un rischio grave e specifico;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; f)
richiede&nbsp;&nbsp; l'osservanza&nbsp;&nbsp; da&nbsp;&nbsp; parte&nbsp;
dei&nbsp; singoli</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>lavoratori&nbsp; delle norme vigenti,
<span class=GramE>nonché</span> delle disposizioni</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>aziendali&nbsp;
in materia di sicurezza e di igiene del lavoro e</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>di uso dei mezzi
di protezione collettivi e dei dispositivi</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>
</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>di protezione
individuali messi a loro disposizione;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; g)
richiede&nbsp;&nbsp; l'osservanza&nbsp;&nbsp; da&nbsp;&nbsp; parte&nbsp;&nbsp;
del&nbsp; medico</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>competente&nbsp; degli&nbsp;
obblighi&nbsp; previsti dal presente decreto, informandolo&nbsp;&nbsp;
sui&nbsp;&nbsp; processi&nbsp;&nbsp; e&nbsp;&nbsp; sui&nbsp;&nbsp;
rischi&nbsp;&nbsp; connessi</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>all'attività' <span class=GramE>produttiva</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; h) adotta le
misure per il controllo delle situazioni</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>di&nbsp; rischio in caso <span
class=GramE>di </span>emergenza e da' istruzioni affinché</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>i&nbsp;
lavoratori,&nbsp; in&nbsp; caso&nbsp; di&nbsp; pericolo&nbsp; grave, immediato
ed</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>inevitabile,&nbsp; abbandonino&nbsp; il&nbsp; posto&nbsp;
di&nbsp; lavoro&nbsp; o la zona</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>pericolosa;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; i) <span
class=GramE>informa</span>&nbsp; il&nbsp; più&nbsp; presto&nbsp;
possibile&nbsp; i lavoratori</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>esposti&nbsp; al&nbsp; rischio di un
pericolo grave e immediato circa</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>il&nbsp; rischio stesso e le
disposizioni prese o da prendere in</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>materia di protezione;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; l)&nbsp; si
astiene, salvo eccezioni debitamente motivate,</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>dal&nbsp;&nbsp;
richiedere&nbsp;&nbsp; ai&nbsp; lavoratori&nbsp; di&nbsp; riprendere&nbsp;
la&nbsp; loro</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>attività&nbsp; in&nbsp; una&nbsp;
situazione di lavoro in cui persiste un</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>pericolo grave e immediato;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; m) permette&nbsp;
ai lavoratori di verificare, mediante il</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>rappresentante&nbsp;&nbsp; per&nbsp;
la&nbsp; sicurezza<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; l'applicazione&nbsp; delle</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>misure
di sicurezza e di protezione della salute e consente</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>al&nbsp;&nbsp;
rappresentante&nbsp; per&nbsp; la&nbsp; sicurezza&nbsp; di&nbsp; accedere&nbsp;
alle</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>informazioni&nbsp;&nbsp; ed&nbsp; alla&nbsp;
documentazione&nbsp; aziendale&nbsp; di&nbsp; cui</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>all'art. 19,
comma 1, lettera e);</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; n) prende&nbsp;
appropriati&nbsp; provvedimenti per evitare che le&nbsp; misure&nbsp; tecniche
adottate possano causare rischi per la&nbsp; salute della popolazione o
deteriorare l'ambiente esterno;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=GramE>o</span>)
tiene&nbsp;&nbsp; un&nbsp;&nbsp; registro&nbsp;&nbsp; nel&nbsp; quale&nbsp;
sono&nbsp; annotati cronologicamente&nbsp; gli&nbsp; infortuni&nbsp; sul lavoro
che comportano un'assenza&nbsp; dal&nbsp; lavoro&nbsp; di&nbsp; almeno un
giorno. Nel registro sono&nbsp;&nbsp; annotati&nbsp;&nbsp; il&nbsp;&nbsp; nome<span
class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; il&nbsp;&nbsp; cognome,&nbsp; la&nbsp;
qualifica professionale&nbsp; dell'infortunato,&nbsp; le cause e le circostanze
dell'infortunio,&nbsp; nonché la data di abbandono e di ripresa del lavoro. Il
registro e' redatto conformemente al modello approvato&nbsp; con&nbsp; decreto
&nbsp;del&nbsp; Ministero&nbsp; del lavoro e della previdenza&nbsp;&nbsp;
sociale<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; sentita&nbsp; la&nbsp; commissione&nbsp;
consultiva permanente,&nbsp; di cui all'art. 393 del decreto del Presidente
della&nbsp; Repubblica&nbsp; 27 aprile&nbsp; 1955,&nbsp; n.&nbsp; 547,&nbsp; e
successive&nbsp; modifiche,&nbsp;&nbsp; ed&nbsp; e'&nbsp; conservato&nbsp;
sul&nbsp; luogo&nbsp; di&nbsp; lavoro,&nbsp; a disposizione&nbsp; dell'organo
di vigilanza. Fino all'emanazione di&nbsp; tale&nbsp; <span class=GramE>decreto&nbsp;
il registro e'</span> redatto in conformità ai modelli gia disciplinati dalle
leggi vigenti;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; p) consulta&nbsp;
il&nbsp; rappresentante&nbsp; per la sicurezza nei casi previsti <span
class=GramE>dall'art. 19, comma 1</span>, lettere b), c) e d);</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; q)
adotta&nbsp;&nbsp; le&nbsp;&nbsp; misure&nbsp;&nbsp; necessarie&nbsp; ai&nbsp;
fini&nbsp; della prevenzione&nbsp; incendi&nbsp; e&nbsp; dell'evacuazione&nbsp;
dei&nbsp; lavoratori, <span class=GramE>nonché</span>&nbsp; per&nbsp; il&nbsp;
caso&nbsp; di pericolo grave e immediato. Tali misure&nbsp; devono&nbsp; essere
adeguate alla natura dell'attività', alle&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
dimensioni&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; dell'azienda<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
ovvero&nbsp;&nbsp; dell'unita' produttiva, e al numero delle persone presenti.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>6.&nbsp; Il&nbsp; datore di lavoro <span
class=GramE>effettua</span> la valutazione di cui al&nbsp; comma&nbsp; 1&nbsp;
ed elabora il documento di cui al comma 2, in collaborazione&nbsp;&nbsp;
con&nbsp;&nbsp; il&nbsp;&nbsp; responsabile&nbsp; del&nbsp; servizio&nbsp; di
prevenzione&nbsp; e&nbsp; protezione&nbsp; e&nbsp; con il medico competente nei
casi&nbsp; in&nbsp; cui&nbsp; sia&nbsp; obbligatoria la sorveglianza sanitaria,
previa consultazione del rappresentante per la sicurezza.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>7.&nbsp; La&nbsp; valutazione di cui
al comma 1 e il documento di cui&nbsp; al&nbsp; comma 2 sono rielaborati in
occasione di modifiche del&nbsp;&nbsp; processo&nbsp;&nbsp; produttivo&nbsp; <span
class=GramE>significative</span>&nbsp; ai&nbsp; fini&nbsp; della sicurezza e
della salute dei lavoratori.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>8.&nbsp; Il&nbsp; datore&nbsp;
di&nbsp; lavoro custodisce, presso l'azienda ovvero&nbsp; l'unita'&nbsp;
produttiva<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; la&nbsp; cartella&nbsp; sanitaria e
di rischio del lavoratore sottoposto a sorveglianza sanitaria, con&nbsp;
salvaguardia&nbsp; del segreto professionale, e ne consegna copia al lavoratore
stesso al momento della risoluzione del rapporto&nbsp;&nbsp; di&nbsp;&nbsp;
lavoro,&nbsp; ovvero&nbsp; quando&nbsp; lo&nbsp; stesso&nbsp; ne&nbsp; fa richiesta.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>9.&nbsp; Per&nbsp; le&nbsp;
piccole&nbsp; e&nbsp; medie&nbsp; aziende, con uno o più decreti&nbsp; da&nbsp;
emanarsi&nbsp; entro&nbsp; il 31 marzo 1996 da parte dei Ministri&nbsp;&nbsp;
del&nbsp;&nbsp; lavoro&nbsp;&nbsp; e&nbsp;&nbsp; della&nbsp;&nbsp; previdenza&nbsp;&nbsp;
sociale, dell'industria<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; del&nbsp;
commercio&nbsp; e dell'artigianato e della sanità,&nbsp; sentita&nbsp; la
commissione consultiva permanente per la&nbsp; prevenzione&nbsp; degli
infortuni e per l'igiene del lavoro,</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>in&nbsp; relazione&nbsp; alla&nbsp;
natura&nbsp; dei&nbsp; rischi&nbsp; e alle dimensioni dell'azienda,&nbsp;
sono&nbsp; definite&nbsp; procedure standardizzate per&nbsp; gli&nbsp;
adempimenti&nbsp; documentali&nbsp; di cui al presente articolo.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Tali&nbsp;&nbsp;
disposizioni&nbsp;&nbsp; non&nbsp;&nbsp; si&nbsp;&nbsp; applicano&nbsp;
alle&nbsp; attività industriali&nbsp; di&nbsp; cui&nbsp; all'art. 1 del decreto
del Presidente della&nbsp; Repubblica&nbsp; 17 maggio&nbsp; 1988<span
class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; n.&nbsp; 175,&nbsp; e successive modifiche, soggette
all'obbligo di dichiarazione o notifica ai&nbsp; sensi&nbsp; degli&nbsp;
articoli 4&nbsp; e&nbsp; 6 del decreto stesso, alle centrali&nbsp;&nbsp;
termoelettriche,&nbsp;&nbsp; agli&nbsp; impianti&nbsp; e&nbsp; laboratori
nucleari,&nbsp;&nbsp; alle&nbsp; aziende&nbsp; estrattive&nbsp; ed&nbsp;
altre&nbsp; attività</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>minerarie,&nbsp; alle aziende per la
fabbricazione e il deposito separato&nbsp;&nbsp; di&nbsp;&nbsp;
esplosivi,&nbsp; polveri&nbsp; e&nbsp; munizioni,&nbsp; e&nbsp; alle strutture
di ricovero e cura sia pubbliche sia private.</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>10.&nbsp; Per&nbsp; le&nbsp; medesime
aziende di cui al comma 9, primo&nbsp;periodo<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;
con&nbsp; uno o più decreti dei Ministri del lavoro e della&nbsp;
previdenza&nbsp; sociale, dell'industria, del commercio e
dell'artigianato&nbsp; e&nbsp; della&nbsp; sanità, sentita la commissione
consultiva&nbsp; permanente per la prevenzione degli infortuni e per l'igiene
del lavoro, possono essere altresì definiti:</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a) i casi <span
class=GramE>relativi a</span> ipotesi di scarsa pericolosità,</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>nei&nbsp;
quali&nbsp; e' possibile lo svolgimento diretto dei compiti di&nbsp;
prevenzione&nbsp; e&nbsp; protezione&nbsp; in&nbsp; aziende&nbsp; ovvero&nbsp;
unità produttive&nbsp; che&nbsp; impiegano un numero di addetti superiore a</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>quello
indicato nell'allegato I;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; b) i casi in cui
e' possibile la riduzione <span class=GramE>a</span> una sola volta all'anno
della visita di cui all'art. 17, lettera h), degli&nbsp; ambienti&nbsp;
di&nbsp; lavoro da parte del medico competente, ferma&nbsp;restando&nbsp;
l'obbligatorietà'&nbsp; di&nbsp; visite&nbsp; ulteriori,</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>allorché
si modificano le situazioni di rischio.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>11.&nbsp; Fatta eccezione per le
aziende indicate nella nota</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>[1]&nbsp; dell'allegato&nbsp; I<span
class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; il&nbsp; datore&nbsp; di lavoro delle aziende
familiari,&nbsp; nonché delle aziende che occupano fino a dieci</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:
Arial'> addetti&nbsp; non&nbsp; e' soggetto agli obblighi di cui ai commi 2 e</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>3,&nbsp;
ma&nbsp; e'&nbsp; tenuto comunque ad autocertificare per iscritto&nbsp;
l'avvenuta&nbsp; effettuazione&nbsp; della&nbsp; valutazione&nbsp; dei rischi e
l'adempimento&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; degli&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; obblighi&nbsp;&nbsp;
ad&nbsp;&nbsp; essa&nbsp;&nbsp; collegati.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>
</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>L'autocertificazione&nbsp;
deve essere inviata al rappresentante</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'> per&nbsp; la sicurezza. Sono <span
class=GramE>in ogni caso soggette</span> agli obblighi di&nbsp; cui&nbsp;
ai&nbsp; commi&nbsp; 2&nbsp; e&nbsp; 3 le aziende familiari nonché le</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:
Arial'> aziende&nbsp; che&nbsp; occupano&nbsp; fino&nbsp; a&nbsp; dieci&nbsp;
addetti, soggette a</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'> particolari&nbsp; fattori di
rischio, individuate nell'ambito di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'> specifici&nbsp; settori&nbsp;
produttivi&nbsp; con&nbsp; uno o più decreti del</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'> Ministro
del lavoro e della previdenza sociale, di concerto</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:
Arial'> con i Ministri della sanità, dell'industria, del commercio</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:
Arial'> e&nbsp; dell'artigianato,&nbsp; delle&nbsp; risorse&nbsp; agricole
alimentari e</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'> forestali&nbsp;&nbsp; e&nbsp;&nbsp;
dell'interno,&nbsp;&nbsp; per&nbsp; quanto&nbsp; di&nbsp; rispettiva competenza.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>12. Gli obblighi <span class=GramE>relativi
agli</span> interventi strutturali e di&nbsp; manutenzione&nbsp;
necessari&nbsp; per&nbsp; assicurare,&nbsp; ai sensi del</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:
Arial'> presente&nbsp; decreto,&nbsp; la sicurezza dei locali e degli edifici</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:
Arial'> assegnati&nbsp; in&nbsp; uso a pubbliche amministrazioni o a pubblici</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:
Arial'> uffici,&nbsp;&nbsp; ivi&nbsp;&nbsp; comprese&nbsp;&nbsp; le&nbsp;
istituzioni&nbsp; scolastiche&nbsp; ed</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'> educative,&nbsp; restano&nbsp;
a&nbsp; carico dell'amministrazione tenuta,</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'> per&nbsp; effetto&nbsp; di norme o
convenzioni, alla loro fornitura e&nbsp; manutenzione.&nbsp;&nbsp; In&nbsp;
tal&nbsp; caso&nbsp; gli&nbsp; obblighi&nbsp; previsti&nbsp; dal</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:
Arial'> presente&nbsp; decreto, relativamente ai predetti interventi, si</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:
Arial'> intendono&nbsp; assolti,&nbsp; da&nbsp; parte&nbsp; dei&nbsp; dirigenti
o funzionari</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'> preposti agli uffici interessati,
con la richiesta del loro</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'> adempimento&nbsp;
all'amministrazione&nbsp; competente&nbsp; o al soggetto che ne ha l'obbligo
giuridico.».</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<pre style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></pre><pre
style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></pre><pre
style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></pre>

<p style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Capo
IV<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>STIMA
DEI COSTI DELLA SICUREZZA </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Art. 7.</span></b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Stima dei costi
della sicurezza</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>1.&nbsp; Ove&nbsp;
e'&nbsp; prevista&nbsp; la&nbsp; redazione&nbsp; del&nbsp; PSC ai sensi del
decreto</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>legislativo&nbsp; 14
agosto&nbsp; 1996, n. 494, e successive modificazioni, nei</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>costi&nbsp; della&nbsp; sicurezza&nbsp; vanno&nbsp;
stimati<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; per&nbsp; tutta&nbsp; la durata delle</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>lavorazioni previste nel cantiere, i costi:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
a) degli apprestamenti previsti <span class=GramE>nel</span> PSC;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
b) delle&nbsp; misure&nbsp; preventive&nbsp; e&nbsp; protettive&nbsp; e dei
dispositivi di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>protezione
individuale eventualmente previsti <span class=GramE>nel</span> PSC per
lavorazioni</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>interferenti;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
c) degli&nbsp; impianti&nbsp; di&nbsp; terra&nbsp; e di protezione contro le
scariche</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>atmosferiche<span
class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; degli&nbsp;&nbsp; impianti&nbsp;&nbsp;
antincendio,&nbsp;&nbsp; degli&nbsp; impianti&nbsp; di</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>evacuazione fumi;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
d) dei mezzi e servizi di protezione collettiva;</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span
class=GramE>e) delle&nbsp; procedure&nbsp; contenute&nbsp; nel&nbsp; PSC e
previste per specifici<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>motivi
di sicurezza;</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span
class=GramE>f) degli&nbsp;&nbsp; eventuali&nbsp; interventi&nbsp;
finalizzati&nbsp; alla&nbsp; sicurezza&nbsp; e<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
</span>richiesti&nbsp; per&nbsp; lo&nbsp; sfasamento spaziale o temporale delle
lavorazioni<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>inte</span>rferenti;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
g) delle&nbsp; misure&nbsp; di&nbsp; coordinamento&nbsp; relative&nbsp;
all'uso&nbsp; comune <span class=GramE>di<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
</span></span>apprestamenti,&nbsp; attrezzature,&nbsp; infrastrutture,&nbsp;
mezzi&nbsp; e&nbsp; servizi&nbsp; di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>protezione collettiva.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>2.&nbsp; Per&nbsp;
le&nbsp; opere rientranti nel campo <span class=GramE>di </span>applicazione
della legge</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>11 febbraio&nbsp;
1994, n. 109, e successive modificazioni, e per le quali</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>non e' prevista la redazione del PSC ai
sensi del decreto legislativo</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>14
agosto&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1996,&nbsp;&nbsp; n.&nbsp;&nbsp; 494,&nbsp;&nbsp;
e&nbsp;&nbsp; successive&nbsp;&nbsp; modificazioni,&nbsp;&nbsp; le</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>amministrazioni&nbsp; appaltanti,&nbsp;
nei&nbsp; costi della sicurezza stimano, per</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>tutta&nbsp; la&nbsp; durata&nbsp; delle&nbsp;
lavorazioni&nbsp; previste nel cantiere, i costi</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>delle&nbsp; misure&nbsp; preventive&nbsp; e&nbsp; protettive
finalizzate alla sicurezza e</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>salute
dei lavoratori.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>3.&nbsp; La&nbsp;
stima&nbsp; dovrà essere congrua, analitica per voci singole, a</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>corpo&nbsp;&nbsp; o&nbsp;&nbsp;
a&nbsp;&nbsp; misura<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;&nbsp; riferita&nbsp;&nbsp;
ad&nbsp; elenchi&nbsp; prezzi&nbsp; standard&nbsp; o</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>specializzati, oppure basata su prezziari o
listini ufficiali vigenti</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>
</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>nell'area
interessata, o sull'elenco prezzi delle misure di sicurezza</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>del committente; nel caso in cui un elenco
prezzi non sia applicabile</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>
</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>o&nbsp;
non&nbsp; disponibile, si farà riferimento ad analisi costi complete e</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>desunte&nbsp; da&nbsp; indagini&nbsp;
di&nbsp; mercato.&nbsp; Le&nbsp; singole voci dei costi della</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>sicurezza&nbsp; vanno calcolate
considerando il loro costo di utilizzo per</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>il cantiere interessato che comprende, quando applicabile,
la posa in</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>opera&nbsp;&nbsp;
ed&nbsp; il&nbsp; successivo&nbsp; smontaggio,&nbsp; l'eventuale&nbsp;
manutenzione&nbsp; e</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>l'ammortamento.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>4.&nbsp; I&nbsp;
costi&nbsp; della&nbsp; sicurezza&nbsp; così&nbsp; individuati<span
class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; sono&nbsp; compresi</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>nell'importo&nbsp; totale&nbsp; dei&nbsp; lavori,&nbsp; ed
individuano la parte del costo</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>dell'opera&nbsp;
da non assoggettare a ribasso nelle offerte delle imprese</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>esecutrici.</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>5.&nbsp; Per la
stima dei costi della sicurezza <span class=GramE>relativi a</span> lavori che
si</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>rendono&nbsp;
necessari&nbsp; a&nbsp; causa&nbsp; di&nbsp; varianti&nbsp; in corso d'opera
previste</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>dall'articolo&nbsp;
25&nbsp; della legge 11 febbraio 1994, n. 109, e successive</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>modificazioni, o dovuti alle variazioni
previste dagli articoli 1659,</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>1660,&nbsp;
1661 e 1664, secondo comma, del codice civile, si applicano le</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>disposizioni&nbsp; contenute&nbsp;
nei&nbsp; commi 1, 2 e 3. I costi della sicurezza</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>così&nbsp; individuati, sono compresi nell'importo totale
della variante,</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>ed&nbsp;
individuano&nbsp; la&nbsp; parte del costo dell'opera da non assoggettare a</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>ribasso.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>6.&nbsp; Il&nbsp;
direttore&nbsp; dei&nbsp; lavori&nbsp; liquida l'importo relativo ai costi</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>della&nbsp; sicurezza&nbsp; previsti&nbsp;
in base allo stato <span class=GramE>di </span>avanzamento lavori,</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>sentito il coordinatore per l'esecuzione
dei lavori quando previsto.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Il presente decreto,
munito del sigillo dello Stato, sarà inserito</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>nella&nbsp; Raccolta&nbsp; ufficiale&nbsp; degli&nbsp;
atti&nbsp; normativi&nbsp; della&nbsp; Repubblica</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>italiana. <span class=GramE>E' fatto obbligo a chiunque
spetti</span> di osservarlo e di farlo</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>osservare.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Dato a Roma, <span
class=SpellE>addi'</span> 3 luglio 2003</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>CIAMPI</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
class=SpellE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Berlusconi</span></span><span
class=GramE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>,</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;
Presidente&nbsp; del&nbsp; Consiglio</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>dei Ministri</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
class=SpellE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Maroni</span></span><span
class=GramE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>,</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;
Ministro&nbsp; del&nbsp; lavoro&nbsp; e delle</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>politiche sociali</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
class=SpellE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Sirchia</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>, Ministro della
salute</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
class=SpellE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Lunardi</span></span><span
class=GramE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>,</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp; Ministro
delle infrastrutture</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>e dei trasporti</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
class=SpellE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Buttiglione</span></span><span
class=GramE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>,</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp; Ministro per
le politiche</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>comunitarie</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
